  "notes": [
    "SMB v1 is the traditional Windows file sharing protocol",
    "32-byte fixed header + word_count(1) + parameter_words + byte_count(2) + data",
    "Uses little-endian byte order",
    "Gradually being replaced by SMB2/SMB3",
    "Common commands: 0x72=Negotiate, 0x73=Session Setup, 0x75=Tree Connect"
